、融通未来。 总台龙年春晚将以「龘龘」之姿，在辞旧迎新的除夕夜陪伴全球华人一起开心、一起互动、一起过年，一起迈进生机盎然、充满希望的甲辰龙年。 央视新闻：龙行龘龘！2024 年总台春晚主题、主标识正式发布"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632935331"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7q30le3nq7s6EAMaCTEwMjkzMDc0OCCEk6qrBjAAOChAInIJNjMyOTM1MzMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1701483376.859302", "card_id": "Q_632927253", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 14}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国气象局发布大地磁暴预警，卫星导航设备误差增大，航空飞行将面临通信环境变差风险，还有哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "根据中国气象局空间天气中心监测，12 月 1 日、 2 日，我国将可能出现地磁暴活动，其中 12 月 1 日可能发生中等以上地磁暴甚至大地磁暴，预计地磁活动将延续到 12 月 2 日。在此影响之下，空间站可能因大气拖拽造成轨道高度下降，卫星导航设备误差增大，航空飞行将面临通信环境变差和跨极区辐射的双重风险，对于公众，尤其是信鸽玩家和极光爱好者，未来几天要时刻注意空间天气信息。中国气象局发布大地磁暴预警 _ 澎湃财讯 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632927253"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7q30le3nq7s6EAMaCTEwMjkyODk4MSD52qmrBjAAOBFAI3IJNjMyOTI3MjUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1701483376.859874", "card_id": "Q_630157182", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 205}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年年轻人存不下钱，而居民的储蓄又持续增长，年轻人的钱去哪儿了？如何解释这一矛盾现象？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-477be00d77a118f31f0e28edfe12514c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630157182"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7q30le3nq7s6EAMaCTEwMjMxMzQz